1
00:00:07,260 --> 00:00:10,700
Have you ever heard about that

2
00:00:10,700 --> 00:00:13,580
the cliff of a snow mountain

3
00:00:14,100 --> 00:00:19,220
once fascinated numerous people?

4
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:24,140
Legend has it that,

5
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,940
there were treasures at the peak

6
00:00:27,780 --> 00:00:32,860
but also there was a bottomless chasm hidden over there.

7
00:00:34,460 --> 00:00:37,900
The smart, the fool

8
00:00:37,940 --> 00:00:40,740
and the kind people,

9
00:00:41,380 --> 00:00:47,220
all are familiar to you.

10
00:00:48,100 --> 00:00:51,660
On the mountainside, on the cliff,

11
00:00:51,980 --> 00:00:54,580
on the cloud,

12
00:00:54,980 --> 00:01:00,100
and in the human world,

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:19,220
snowflakes are drifting profusely and disorderly.

14
00:01:30,980 --> 00:01:34,980
Joy of Life Season 1

15
00:01:34,980 --> 00:01:37,900
Episode 33

16
00:01:39,550 --> 00:01:40,830
Smash it at critical moment.

17
00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:42,630
It won't take any lives

18
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,590
or hurt anyone physically,

19
00:01:45,230 --> 00:01:46,910
but even Great Masters

20
00:01:46,910 --> 00:01:48,040
will sleep quite a while from it.

21
00:01:48,950 --> 00:01:49,720
Thank you, Teacher!

22
00:01:49,870 --> 00:01:50,510
No problem.

23
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,440
Just don't show off with it.

24
00:02:08,620 --> 00:02:09,660
=Si Lili, courtesan of Joy Tsin House=

25
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,240
The little emperor clearly requires

26
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:23,630
to send Si Lili back to Beiqi.

27
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:27,190
Do they have any private relationship?

28
00:02:34,670 --> 00:02:35,630
Don't stare at her!

29
00:02:36,270 --> 00:02:37,470
The curtain is specially made.

30
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:38,910
She can't hear what we're talking about.

31
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:41,000
It doesn't make sense.

32
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:42,600
If the little emperor

33
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:43,630
really has a private relationship with her,

34
00:02:43,630 --> 00:02:44,910
why did he send her to the capital city

35
00:02:44,910 --> 00:02:45,800
as a secret agent?

36
00:03:21,260 --> 00:03:23,260
=Investigator's Office=

37
00:03:26,910 --> 00:03:27,800
Here comes Xiao En.

38
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:55,620
=Xiao En, former Head of the Beiqi agents=

39
00:03:55,620 --> 00:03:57,110
The smell of sunlight.

40
00:04:00,110 --> 00:04:02,520
Go! Go! Hurry!

41
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:10,160
Do you have family?

42
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,240
Tell them to stay alive.

43
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:14,240
I will find them.

44
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,390
It's your luck to get out.

45
00:04:16,830 --> 00:04:19,040
Don't irritate the descendants at this time.

46
00:04:19,550 --> 00:04:20,790
You'll regret it

47
00:04:21,390 --> 00:04:22,350
if he kills you by mistake.

48
00:04:22,350 --> 00:04:23,550
If I'm killed,

49
00:04:23,550 --> 00:04:24,880
so will be you son.

50
00:04:26,510 --> 00:04:27,880
You'll regret that.

51
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:31,480
Then stay alive and stop flaunting.

52
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:35,000
Otherwise the Investigator's Office will catch you again.

53
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,440
Chen Pingping!

54
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:45,000
Fei Jie!

55
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,230
You are still alive.

56
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:51,000
Very good!

57
00:04:52,550 --> 00:04:53,790
I prayed in there that

58
00:04:53,790 --> 00:04:55,160
you can live a long life

59
00:04:56,230 --> 00:04:57,720
so that I can still have the chance of finding you.

60
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,440
I'll make you dumb with my poison

61
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:59,350
if you keep talking rubbish.

62
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,480
Try it!

63
00:05:03,390 --> 00:05:04,790
My son was poisoned to death

64
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:07,600
by you in the end.

65
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:10,390
What was the poison?

66
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:12,790
Do you still have it?

67
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,790
What are you laughing at?

68
00:05:20,790 --> 00:05:21,950
What is he laughing at?

69
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,790
I'm laughing at your legs.

70
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,480
They're destroyed by me.

71
00:05:29,670 --> 00:05:32,040
I thought you are laughing at yourself.

72
00:05:33,110 --> 00:05:35,270
As a loser being imprisoned in jail

73
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:36,350
for so many years

74
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:38,550
who couldn't move an inch,

75
00:05:39,350 --> 00:05:40,830
do you feel very comfortable?

76
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,270
Hold him!

77
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:53,670
You're old now.

78
00:05:54,350 --> 00:05:55,670
Control your temper

79
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,040
and care for your own health.

80
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,880
Do you really let me go back?

81
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,270
Do you really want to stay?

82
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:07,760
You'll regret it.

83
00:06:14,830 --> 00:06:17,510
He is Fan Xian, Director-General of the Investigator's Office.

84
00:06:17,550 --> 00:06:18,390
He'll escort you.

85
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:22,950
Nice to see you, Senor Xiao. How are you doing?

86
00:06:24,070 --> 00:06:25,040
Are you going to escort me?

87
00:06:25,270 --> 00:06:26,000
Yup!

88
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:27,390
Who are these people to you?

89
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:29,480
Master Fei is my teacher.

90
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,920
The Head is my senior friend.

91
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,440
They all treat me like families.

92
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,670
Take a good look at this kid.

93
00:06:35,510 --> 00:06:36,950
This will be your last chance.

94
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:39,320
You should take a good look at this yard,

95
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,550
as you may come back again in the future.

96
00:06:46,110 --> 00:06:50,000
Be careful on the way. You're still too young.

97
00:06:50,270 --> 00:06:51,390
I'll learn from you.

98
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,070
Fan Xian,

99
00:07:09,550 --> 00:07:11,320
the mission and your carriage

100
00:07:11,510 --> 00:07:13,270
are meeting you outside the city.

101
00:07:14,110 --> 00:07:14,880
Thank you!

102
00:07:15,110 --> 00:07:15,880
Please trust me.

103
00:07:16,350 --> 00:07:17,480
I'll surely bring your son back safely

104
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,670
to the capital city.

105
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:25,880
Fan Xian,

106
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:28,270
let's go! I'll walk you there.

107
00:07:28,510 --> 00:07:29,350
You go first.

108
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:31,070
I need to talk to him in private.

109
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,640
Send your teacher back early.

110
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,510
He's got injury on his body.

111
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:55,760
What?

112
00:07:56,390 --> 00:07:57,440
He had a sticky fight

113
00:07:58,390 --> 00:08:01,110
against the Embroidered Uniform
Guards of Shen Zhong in Beiqi.

114
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:03,550
Upon hearing that you're going to Beiqi,

115
00:08:04,070 --> 00:08:05,110
he rode the horse for 800 miles

116
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,110
to get back to the capital city

117
00:08:07,550 --> 00:08:09,510
and experienced six assassinations,

118
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,440
but he didn't stop for any single minute.

119
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:15,350
He wasn't like this in the past.

120
00:08:17,510 --> 00:08:18,390
Your appearance

121
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:22,070
changed us both.

122
00:08:23,790 --> 00:08:24,790
He should take a rest.

123
00:08:24,790 --> 00:08:25,510
Let me get him back.

124
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,110
Go to the Taiping Residence.

125
00:08:29,390 --> 00:08:30,350
Someone wants to see you.

126
00:08:54,860 --> 00:08:58,100
=Taiping Residence=

127
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:11,760
It could have not been you

128
00:09:12,150 --> 00:09:13,880
to lead the mission to Beiqi this time.

129
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:15,760
Then why is it me in the end?

130
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:19,960
You're young. You should take up the challenge

131
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,590
to cultivate your mind and intelligence.

132
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:24,960
Your Majesty think I have mental defects?

133
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:29,670
Do you know

134
00:09:29,710 --> 00:09:30,670
what the missions are this time?

135
00:09:31,230 --> 00:09:32,670
I heard there are a few,

136
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,030
but I am only told

137
00:09:35,030 --> 00:09:36,440
to get Yan Bingyun back.

138
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:38,230
Nothing else.

139
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:40,400
Are my missions

140
00:09:40,670 --> 00:09:42,200
assigned by Your Majesty in person?

141
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:46,080
They poisoned Si Lili.

142
00:09:46,670 --> 00:09:48,320
Do they mean to kill her on the way?

143
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:49,910
She won't die.

144
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:53,470
She is not the target. Someone else is!

145
00:09:53,910 --> 00:09:55,550
It's prepared for the little emperor of Beiqi?

146
00:09:58,590 --> 00:10:01,520
This plan is called Red Sleeve Edict.

147
00:10:02,550 --> 00:10:04,280
I'm afraid it's a death edict.

148
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:05,840
After getting Yan Bingyun back,

149
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:09,200
find a chance to kill Xiao En.

150
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:12,590
You want me

151
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:13,710
to kill Xiao En

152
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,230
under the eyes of the Beiqi people?

153
00:10:16,030 --> 00:10:17,080
There doesn't seem to be anything else

154
00:10:17,590 --> 00:10:18,880
other than that.

155
00:10:22,550 --> 00:10:23,590
Kill the emperor and Xiao En

156
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:27,030
in an alien state.

157
00:10:28,550 --> 00:10:29,960
This is thrilling enough.

158
00:10:31,640 --> 00:10:33,030
And I can tell you

159
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,840
the Investigator's Office won't help you

160
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:39,080
as it may become suspicious as a result.

161
00:10:39,550 --> 00:10:41,080
Your Majesty really flattered me.

162
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:42,760
What else do you have to say?

163
00:10:43,670 --> 00:10:45,110
I do have a doubt.

164
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:45,840
Say it!

165
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:47,470
You can talk to me in the palace as well.

166
00:10:47,470 --> 00:10:48,590
Why do you choose here?

167
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,440
This is different from the palace.

168
00:10:50,590 --> 00:10:51,710
We're in the monarch-subject relationship in palace,

169
00:10:51,710 --> 00:10:52,320
but here...

170
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,000
What's the difference?

171
00:10:57,670 --> 00:10:58,910
Come back alive.

172
00:11:00,470 --> 00:11:02,880
What did you just say, Your Majesty?

173
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,670
Remember to come back alive.

174
00:11:04,710 --> 00:11:05,640
It doesn't matter

175
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:06,280
even if the mission fails

176
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:07,400
as long as I can come back alive?

177
00:11:07,470 --> 00:11:09,350
Don't ask while knowing the answer.

178
00:11:11,110 --> 00:11:12,590
This is my order!

179
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:14,590
Piss off!

180
00:11:52,230 --> 00:11:54,350
There is merely monarch-subject relationship in the palace.

181
00:11:54,670 --> 00:11:55,590
How different is it

182
00:11:55,590 --> 00:11:56,790
in Taiping Residence?

183
00:11:57,520 --> 00:11:58,520
You've met His Majesty?

184
00:11:59,230 --> 00:12:00,880
I felt like I've met a fake emperor.

185
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:02,520
Do you think it's a bit difficult

186
00:12:03,110 --> 00:12:04,710
about the mission this time?

187
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:05,520
Not really!

188
00:12:05,710 --> 00:12:06,550
Don't worry, Teacher.

189
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:09,470
Initially, I wanted to go to Beiqi

190
00:12:09,470 --> 00:12:10,640
along with you.

191
00:12:10,640 --> 00:12:11,350
No!

192
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:14,080
Head Chen has also said

193
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:17,320
I have killed too many Beiqi agents.

194
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:19,470
If I go with you,

195
00:12:20,150 --> 00:12:21,320
it may be bad for you.

196
00:12:21,670 --> 00:12:23,280
Just stay in the capital city for a rest.

197
00:12:23,350 --> 00:12:24,200
Wait for my return.

198
00:12:25,400 --> 00:12:26,470
Pay special attention to such a few people

199
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:29,030
when you reach Beiqi.

200
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,200
One is the

201
00:12:31,670 --> 00:12:33,960
Commander-in-chief of Embroidered
Uniform Guards, Shen Zhong.

202
00:12:34,350 --> 00:12:35,590
Head has told me about him.

203
00:12:36,590 --> 00:12:38,000
The other one is Ku He,

204
00:12:38,030 --> 00:12:39,520
the Great Master.

205
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,710
I heard that

206
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:45,320
he doesn't want Xiao En to return to Beiqi.

207
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:46,880
Both of them are Beiqi people, aren't they?

208
00:12:48,590 --> 00:12:50,640
Guo Baokun and you are both Nanqing people.

209
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:52,470
Do you like each other?

210
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:53,790
Good point!

211
00:12:54,790 --> 00:12:55,710
But what can I do

212
00:12:55,710 --> 00:12:57,110
if the Great Master

213
00:12:57,110 --> 00:12:58,350
wants to plot against me?

214
00:12:59,350 --> 00:13:01,230
He'll respect his own identity.

215
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:04,110
If he wants to stop Xiao En to return,

216
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:06,400
he will send his disciples.

217
00:13:08,110 --> 00:13:08,880
Does he have a lot of disciples?

218
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:11,150
None of them matters

219
00:13:11,790 --> 00:13:14,030
except the one

220
00:13:14,030 --> 00:13:15,080
named Haitang.

221
00:13:16,030 --> 00:13:17,320
That sounds like

222
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,110
a lady's name.

223
00:13:18,550 --> 00:13:20,400
Haitang is also named as Haitang Duoduo.

224
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:22,280
She is the last disciple of Ku He.

225
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:23,960
She is

226
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:25,590
a famous talent in Beiqi

227
00:13:26,230 --> 00:13:28,110
where the people respectfully call her the Saintess.

228
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:29,760
So it is a lady!

229
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,760
You're the poetic genius and she is the Saintess.

230
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,320
That's tit for tat.

231
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:35,470
She is said to be ranked as Ninth Dan.

232
00:13:35,910 --> 00:13:37,080
It's quite easy

233
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:37,960
to become a Ninth Dan master, right?

234
00:13:38,110 --> 00:13:39,030
There are just too many!

235
00:13:39,280 --> 00:13:40,910
A Ninth Dan master is easy to defeat,

236
00:13:42,790 --> 00:13:45,400
but if Ku He really wants

237
00:13:45,400 --> 00:13:46,760
to stop Xiao En from going back

238
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:48,760
and does it himself,

239
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:50,440
we'll have to accept it.

240
00:13:53,350 --> 00:13:54,960
Teacher, you know really a lot

241
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:55,840
about Beiqi.

242
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:57,470
Don't flatter me!

243
00:13:58,790 --> 00:13:59,280
There is one more guy

244
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:00,910
who is the general of Beiqi, Shangshan Hu.

245
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:02,790
This guy resists the savages for a number of years

246
00:14:03,280 --> 00:14:04,320
and wins all the battles.

247
00:14:04,640 --> 00:14:06,440
Some said he is bad-tempered.

248
00:14:06,710 --> 00:14:09,320
Some said he is soft and humble.

249
00:14:09,710 --> 00:14:11,030
Isn't that contradictory?

250
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,470
That's the strange part.

251
00:14:13,150 --> 00:14:14,880
Does he have dissociative disorders?

252
00:14:16,550 --> 00:14:18,280
Shangshan Hu is Xiao En's adopted son.

253
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:20,550
He's been looking forward

254
00:14:20,710 --> 00:14:22,440
to the return of Xiao En.

255
00:14:23,110 --> 00:14:23,840
Then it's not likely for him

256
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:24,840
to plot against me.

257
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:26,840
After all, I'm escorting his adoptive father back.

258
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:27,640
Yeah!

259
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:30,590
He should not plot against you.

260
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:36,080
Have you baked the meat?

261
00:14:36,350 --> 00:14:37,280
Where is my meat?

262
00:14:38,150 --> 00:14:38,880
Your Excellency,

263
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:40,110
we have it prepared a long time back.

264
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:53,860
=Shangshan Hu, Grand General of Beiqi=

265
00:15:08,400 --> 00:15:08,960
Grand General,

266
00:15:09,350 --> 00:15:10,670
we got message from Nanqing.

267
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:11,790
The Nanqing mission

268
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:12,960
is sending Mr. Xiao En back.

269
00:15:14,710 --> 00:15:15,880
We can't let my adoptive father

270
00:15:15,910 --> 00:15:17,280
fall in the hands of the throne.

271
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:19,840
Let's meet them in the territory of Nanqing

272
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:21,840
and take over him first.

273
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:23,640
How do we deal with the escorting mission?

274
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:26,840
Who is the leader?

275
00:15:26,910 --> 00:15:29,470
Fan Xian, the poetic genius of Nanqing.

276
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:32,320
I haven't heard of him.

277
00:15:32,790 --> 00:15:33,840
Kill him when they come.

278
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:34,960
Yes!

279
00:15:58,030 --> 00:15:58,760
Teacher,

280
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,110
what's the family name of Shangshan Hu?

281
00:16:00,150 --> 00:16:01,960
Is it Shangshan

282
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:03,110
or Shang?

283
00:16:08,590 --> 00:16:09,520
